## Now you!

-   Split up in groups

-   Come up with a construct you want to measure

-   How would you assess the three types of reliability for the measure?

-   How would you assess the five types of validity of the measure?

-   Incorporate as many insights from the chapter as possible as to what makes a reliable and valid measure
